page.title: 18Wildlife Flowers
page.content: Canal and Riverside_Flag-iris,arrow-head,buckbea n,water-lily,water-crowfoot,celandine, may-flower,saxifrage,cowslip,wood anemone,marsh marigold,sorrel,wood avens,hemlock,cow-parsley,butter-bur,c omfrey,for-get-me-not,monkey flower,brooklime and garlic. Roadside and garden weeds.-Coltsfoot, ox-eye daisy,silver-weed,milfoil, hawkweed,dock,groundsel,bulbous butter cup,shepherd's purse,chickweed,ground elder,nettle and plantain. Pasture and hedgerow._Daisy,clover, buttercup,red campion,trefoil,vetch, meadow-sweet,cinquefoil,lady's mantle, ragwort,knapweed,nipplewort,dandelion, speedwell,bugle,blue-bell,fox-glove, sorrel,primrose,burdock,dog's mercury, ivy-leaved toadflax,pimpernal,thistle, harebell,rosebay willowherb,cleavers and bedstraw.
